## Long to wide


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
dining_long %>% 
  pivot_wider(names_from = restaurant_type, 
              values_from = n_restaurants)
```
:::


**`names_from`** Which columns' values will be used for new *column names*

**`values_from`** Which column has the *cell values* for the new output columns


